LightSquared Inc.’s proposed
auction format for a sale of its wireless spectrum assets is
improper and could foil a $2.22 billion offer from a unit of
Charlie Ergen’s  Dish Network Corp. (DISH) , a group of lenders said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
